{"tid":1377841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近戰抗蓄龍建議收集區","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:53:13.000Z","uid":49270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ccff99d98b06a3325a6fbbd3a4e2ca691473b9","tid":1377841,"uid":49270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"個人建議沙灘水槍好有用<br />\n又平又輕便<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbaZE2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbaZE2j.jpg&h=a42aff4c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n文具鋪玩具鋪可以搵到<br />\n可以入油漆(無人叫你買油性漆搶火,買水性就OK),食用油等液體,夏水禮時必備<br />\n一拉就吸到,一推就噴到<br />\n最前排可以開遮,弓手可以係遮既窿之間發射防止身份暴露<br />\n兜口兜面射可以防止獅子撲兔<br />\n<br />\n之前好多人討論點樣用漆<br />\n用膠袋用水槍用乜<br />\n但呢個方法成本最低又易搵到<br />\n歡迎討論點應對蓄龍"},{"pid":"ed413a4a12dcc8dab55da96949db76f1e37cbeaf","tid":1377841,"uid":49270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}